Baysn is a next-generation Discord moderation bot designed to keep your community safe with zero effort.
Built with a powerful regex automod engine, Baysn detects spam, scams, invite bypasses, and leetspeak patterns that slip past other bots.

⚡ Lightning fast response times (<200ms)

🛡️ Protecting 840,000+ users

📈 99% uptime and reliable infrastructure

🔍 Smart pattern detection (Unicode, character spacing, obfuscation)

Formerly known as MANIAC, Baysn has been rebuilt with speed, reliability, and simplicity at its core.
